                     <interp inst="t18180401-26-person211" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a salesman, and live in Drury-lane. I saw the prisoner take the handkerchief out of Mr. Batt's pocket, and put it up to his nose. Mr. Batt took it from him.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I had been out of employ four months, and did it through distress.</p>
